Preheat oven to 400 degrees F. Cut each bacon slice into 4 pieces. Wrap each Lit'l Smokie with piece of bacon; secure with a toothpick. Place in a 13x9x2 inch baking pan. Sprinkle evenly with brown sugar. Bake for 30 to 35 minutes or until bacon is crisp and sugar is melted. Cool slightly before serving.